{"title":"github+hexo 搭建个人博客","slug":"first-blog","date":"2020-10-14","updated":"2020-12-28","comments":true,"path":"api/posts/50416.json","excerpt":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/siyuanhome/blog/img/github_repo.png","covers":["https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/siyuanhome/blog/img/github_repo.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/siyuanhome/blog/img/github_page.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/siyuanhome/blog/img/ssh_pub.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/siyuanhome/blog/img/ssh1.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/siyuanhome/blog/img/ssh2.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/siyuanhome/blog/img/check_ssh.png","https://siyuanhome.github.io/asset/img/test.png"],"content":"<p><strong><em>前言</em></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>现在国内有很多平台都提供发表博客的服务，零成本，只需要一个账号，并且也不需要搭建维护，博主只管填充内容即可。那么如何看待独立个人博客呢？</li>\n<li>一个域名加上服务器就可以做到，它的自由度很高，不受平台限制，包括可以设计布局。如果内容足够硬核，还会被搜索引擎收录，到时输入关键字，弹出自己的博客，岂不快哉！对于想拥有自己独立博客的朋友，请耐心看下去，我会将搭建过程详细的呈现出来。</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"准备工作\"><a href=\"# 准备工作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"准备工作\"></a>准备工作</h1><blockquote>\n<p>安装环境<br>Linux7.8<br>Node12.13.1<br>Hexo5.2.0<br>Git1.8.3.1</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"github 新建仓库\"><a href=\"#github 新建仓库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"github 新建仓库\"></a>github 新建仓库 </h2><p> 首先需要一个 git 账号，然后创建一个仓库，名字必须是‘用户名.github.io’，设置成公开，注意，以后这个名字就是你的域名了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/siyuanhome/blog/img/github_repo.png\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"开启 GitHub-pages 设置\"><a href=\"# 开启 GitHub-pages 设置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"开启 GitHub pages 设置\"></a>开启 GitHub pages 设置 </h2><p> 这里选择将你的仓库的主分支启用为 Github 页面</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/siyuanhome/blog/img/github_page.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"设置 ssh 免密登录\"><a href=\"# 设置 ssh 免密登录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"设置 ssh 免密登录\"></a>设置 ssh 免密登录</h2><ul>\n<li>首先检查本地是否存在密钥，若有则跳过第一步</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"生成 ssh 密钥，一般在 -ssh 目录下执行\"><a href=\"# 生成 ssh 密钥，一般在 -ssh 目录下执行\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"生成 ssh 密钥，一般在.ssh 目录下执行\"></a>生成 ssh 密钥，一般在.ssh 目录下执行</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sh-keygen -t rsa -b 2048 -f ssh_key -N &#x27;&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"进入后缀名为 -pub 的文件，拷贝公钥信息\"><a href=\"# 进入后缀名为 -pub 的文件，拷贝公钥信息\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"进入后缀名为.pub 的文件，拷贝公钥信息\"></a>进入后缀名为.pub 的文件，拷贝公钥信息</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/siyuanhome/blog/img/ssh_pub.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"进入 github\"><a href=\"# 进入 github\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"进入 github\"></a>进入 github</h3><p>  <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/siyuanhome/blog/img/ssh1.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"将内容粘贴进去，标题自取\"><a href=\"# 将内容粘贴进去，标题自取\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"将内容粘贴进去，标题自取\"></a>将内容粘贴进去，标题自取</h3><p>  <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/siyuanhome/blog/img/ssh2.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"最后验证是否成功\"><a href=\"# 最后验证是否成功\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"最后验证是否成功\"></a>最后验证是否成功</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li><p>若出现下面信息，则设置成功</p>\n<p>  <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/siyuanhome/blog/img/check_ssh.png\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"安装 Node-js\"><a href=\"# 安装 Node-js\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装 Node.js\"></a>安装 Node.js</h1><ul>\n<li>官方网站：<a href=\"http://nodejs.cn/download/\">http://nodejs.cn/download/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget https://npm.taobao.org/mirrors/node/v12.13.1/node-v12.13.1-linux-x64.tar.xz</span><br><span class=\"line\">tar -xvf node-v12.13.1-linux-x64.tar.xz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"修改文件名（可选）\"><a href=\"# 修改文件名（可选）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改文件名（可选）\"></a>修改文件名（可选）</h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mv node-v12.13.1-linux-x64 nodejs</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"检查 node 是否安装成功 - 出现版本号代表成功\"><a href=\"# 检查 node 是否安装成功 - 出现版本号代表成功\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"检查 node 是否安装成功, 出现版本号代表成功\"></a>检查 node 是否安装成功, 出现版本号代表成功</h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cd node-v12.13.1-linux-x64</span><br><span class=\"line\">./bin/node -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"创建 node 和 npm 软链接 -xxx- 为子目录\"><a href=\"# 创建 node 和 npm 软链接 -xxx- 为子目录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建 node 和 npm 软链接 (xxx/ 为子目录)\"></a> 创建 node 和 npm 软链接(xxx/ 为子目录)</h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ln -s /root/xxx//nodejs/bin/node /usr/local/bin/node</span><br><span class=\"line\">ln -s /root/xxx/nodejs/bin/npm /usr/local/bin/npm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"安装及配置 hexo\"><a href=\"# 安装及配置 hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装及配置 hexo\"></a>安装及配置 hexo</h1><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class=\"line\">ln -s /root/xxx//nodejs/lib/node_modules/hexo-cli/bin/hexo /usr/local/bin/hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"检查 hexo 版本\"><a href=\"# 检查 hexo 版本\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"检查 hexo 版本\"></a>检查 hexo 版本</h2><ul>\n<li>若出现下面的信息，则安装成功</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@localhost hexo]# hexo -v</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo: 5.2.0</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo-cli: 4.2.0</span><br><span class=\"line\">os: Linux 3.10.0-1127.el7.x86_64 linux x64</span><br><span class=\"line\">node: 12.13.1</span><br><span class=\"line\">v8: 7.7.299.13-node.16</span><br><span class=\"line\">uv: 1.33.1</span><br><span class=\"line\">zlib: 1.2.11</span><br><span class=\"line\">brotli: 1.0.7</span><br><span class=\"line\">ares: 1.15.0</span><br><span class=\"line\">modules: 72</span><br><span class=\"line\">nghttp2: 1.39.2</span><br><span class=\"line\">napi: 5</span><br><span class=\"line\">llhttp: 1.1.4</span><br><span class=\"line\">http_parser: 2.8.0</span><br><span class=\"line\">openssl: 1.1.1d</span><br><span class=\"line\">cldr: 35.1</span><br><span class=\"line\">icu: 64.2</span><br><span class=\"line\">tz: 2019c</span><br><span class=\"line\">unicode: 12.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"hexo 添加 github 地址\"><a href=\"#hexo 添加 github 地址\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo 添加 github 地址\"></a>hexo 添加 github 地址</h2><ul>\n<li>在测试环境的主目录进入_config.yml 文件，在最后加上 git 服务器地址</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  type: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  repository: git@github.com:boke/boke.github.io.git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"安装 hexo-git 插件\"><a href=\"# 安装 hexo-git 插件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装 hexo git 插件\"></a>安装 hexo git 插件</h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"创建博客测试环境\"><a href=\"# 创建博客测试环境\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建博客测试环境\"></a>创建博客测试环境</h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkdir test</span><br><span class=\"line\">cd test</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo init  #初始化</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"hexo 常用命令\"><a href=\"#hexo 常用命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo 常用命令\"></a>hexo 常用命令</h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo clean   # 清除缓存文件，想要更换主题或重新生成静态文件时可使用</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo new &quot;postName&quot; #新建文章</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo new page &quot;pageName&quot; #新建页面</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo generate   # 生成静态文件</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo server     # 实现本地预览（默认端口 4000，curl+c 退出）</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo deploy     # 上传到 git 服务器</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>缩写：</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo n == hexo new</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo g == hexo generate</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo s == hexo server</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo d == hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>组合命令：</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo s -g #生成并本地预览</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo d -g #生成并上传</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<ul>\n<li>最后在浏览器输入你的域名就会出现测试页面了</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://siyuanhome.github.io/asset/img/test.png\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"报错总结\"><a href=\"# 报错总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"报错总结\"></a>报错总结 </h1><h2 id=\"执行相关命令出现的报错\"><a href=\"# 执行相关命令出现的报错\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"执行相关命令出现的报错\"></a> 执行相关命令出现的报错</h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@localhost hexo]# hexo g</span><br><span class=\"line\">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class=\"line\">INFO  =======================================</span><br><span class=\"line\">██╗ ██████╗ █████╗ ██████╗ ██╗   ██╗███████╗</span><br><span class=\"line\">██║██╔════╝██╔══██╗██╔══██╗██║   ██║██╔════╝</span><br><span class=\"line\">██║██║     ███████║██████╔╝██║   ██║███████╗</span><br><span class=\"line\">██║██║     ██╔══██║██╔══██╗██║   ██║╚════██║</span><br><span class=\"line\">██║╚██████╗██║  ██║██║  ██║╚██████╔╝███████║</span><br><span class=\"line\">╚═╝ ╚═════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝ ╚═════╝ ╚══════╝</span><br><span class=\"line\">=============================================</span><br><span class=\"line\">INFO  === Checking package dependencies ===</span><br><span class=\"line\">ERROR Package bulma-stylus is not installed.</span><br><span class=\"line\">ERROR Package hexo-renderer-inferno is not installed.</span><br><span class=\"line\">ERROR Package hexo-component-inferno is not installed.</span><br><span class=\"line\">ERROR Package inferno is not installed.</span><br><span class=\"line\">ERROR Package inferno-create-element is not installed.</span><br><span class=\"line\">ERROR Please install the missing dependencies your Hexo site root directory:</span><br><span class=\"line\">ERROR npm install --save bulma-stylus@0.8.0 hexo-renderer-inferno@^0.1.3 hexo-component-inferno@^0.10.0 inferno@^7.3.3 inferno-create-element@^7.3.3</span><br><span class=\"line\">ERROR or:</span><br><span class=\"line\">ERROR yarn add bulma-stylus@0.8.0 hexo-renderer-inferno@^0.1.3 hexo-component-inferno@^0.10.0 inferno@^7.3.3 inferno-create-element@^7.3.3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>根据提示安装相关依赖</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install --save bulma-stylus@0.8.0 hexo-renderer-inferno@^0.1.3 hexo-component-inferno@^0.10.0 inferno@^7.3.3 inferno-create-element@^7.3.3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<ul>\n<li>若出现下面错误</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[root@localhost hexo]# hexo d</span><br><span class=\"line\">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class=\"line\">Inferno is in development mode.</span><br><span class=\"line\">INFO  =======================================</span><br><span class=\"line\">██╗ ██████╗ █████╗ ██████╗ ██╗   ██╗███████╗</span><br><span class=\"line\">██║██╔════╝██╔══██╗██╔══██╗██║   ██║██╔════╝</span><br><span class=\"line\">██║██║     ███████║██████╔╝██║   ██║███████╗</span><br><span class=\"line\">██║██║     ██╔══██║██╔══██╗██║   ██║╚════██║</span><br><span class=\"line\">██║╚██████╗██║  ██║██║  ██║╚██████╔╝███████║</span><br><span class=\"line\">╚═╝ ╚═════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝ ╚═════╝ ╚══════╝</span><br><span class=\"line\">=============================================</span><br><span class=\"line\">INFO  === Checking package dependencies ===</span><br><span class=\"line\">INFO  === Checking theme configurations ===</span><br><span class=\"line\">INFO  === Registering Hexo extensions ===</span><br><span class=\"line\">ERROR Deployer not found: git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>则安装 hexo git 插件</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"若执行 hexo-clean 报错\"><a href=\"# 若执行 hexo-clean 报错\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"若执行 hexo clean 报错\"></a>若执行 hexo clean 报错</h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ERROR Local hexo not found in ~/simon</span><br><span class=\"line\">ERROR Try running: &#x27;npm install hexo --save&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>则执行 npm install hexo –save</li>\n<li>再执行 hexo clean</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"执行 hexo-d 上传代码报错\"><a href=\"# 执行 hexo-d 上传代码报错\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"执行 hexo d 上传代码报错\"></a>执行 hexo d 上传代码报错</h2><ul>\n<li>上传代码之前，要在测试环境的主目录进入_config.yml 文件，在最后加上 git 服务器地址</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  type: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  repository: git@github.com:boke/boke.github.io.git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<ul>\n<li>若第一次使用 git，则执行</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git config --global user.name &quot;Your Name&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">git config --global user.email you@example.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>特别注意：yml 文件对格式要求很严格，哪怕一个空格，也不要忽视</strong></p>\n<h1 id=\"扩展\"><a href=\"# 扩展\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"扩展\"></a>扩展</h1><ul>\n<li>hexo 官网主题：<a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\">https://hexo.io/themes/</a></li>\n<li>在线博客编辑工具：<a href=\"http://pandao.github.io/editor.md/\">http://pandao.github.io/editor.md/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>首先找一个自己中意的主题，找到 github 代码库，拷贝 https 地址</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cd test/themes</span><br><span class=\"line\">git clone https://github.com/jinyaoMa/hexo-theme-mustom.git mustom</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>根据其模板的说明文档修改样式和插件</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><strong>修改主配置文件（101 行左右）</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> Extensions</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># Plugins: https://hexo.io/plugins/</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"><span class=\"comment\"># Themes: https://hexo.io/themes/</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">theme: mustom    # themes 目录下的模板的名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><strong>重新启动</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo clean</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo d</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","url":"/posts/50416/","min2read":5,"word4post":"1.3k","prev_post":{"title":"Hello World","url":"/posts/16107/"},"next_post":null,"t